": \"The agent for American rugby player Ilona Maher can barely catch her breath in Paris, where Maher has boosted her initial popularity from three years ago at the Tokyo Games all the way to bona fide stardom.\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999481387944, \"rank\": 4.5518330054935536e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\", \"score\": 0.9999999134151987, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ilona Maher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5223302690438412e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The agent\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"her breath\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"Maher\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"her initial popularity\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"stardom\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maher's savvy use of social media attracted attention in Tokyo but is now at a global level - she has nearly 5.5 million followers across her social media accounts and almost 121 million likes across all her TikToks - and has cultivated a brand.\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9988497919024711, \"rank\": 0.0011511898919420553, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maher's savvy use\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"a global level\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 5.5 million followers\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"her social media accounts\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"almost 121 million likes\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"all her TikToks\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of people see her popping off right now and having this viral moment, but we have been working really strategically to be able to position her to have a lightning in a bottle moment,\\\" said agent Rheann Engelke of Range Sports.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"this viral moment\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"a lightning\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"a bottle moment\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"agent Rheann Engelke\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"Range Sports\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tracking service found that Maher saw a 257% increase in Instagram followers from June 30 to July 30, as she led the United States to its first medal, a bronze, in rugby sevens.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.804396499388407e-39, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999999265583, \"rank\": 4.902150345424965e-10, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A tracking service\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"Maher\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"a 257% increase\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"its first medal\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her crowning athletic achievement and burgeoning fame, the offers began pouring in.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletic achievement\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"burgeoning fame\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"the offers\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maher's platform is focused on body positivity, women empowerment, promoting rugby and encouraging young girls to play sports, but her sharp sense of humor and social media use has brought in dozens of opportunities - including some in the entertainment space.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maher's platform\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2801}, {\"ngram\": \"body positivity\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"young girls\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"her sharp sense\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"humor\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"social media use\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"the entertainment space\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What's really special about Ilona is going into this Olympic moment, she knew exactly who she was, she knew what her message was and she knew the kind of brands she wanted to align with,\\\" Engelke said.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\", \"score\": 0.9999999986521289, \"rank\": 1.3480749850994234e-09, \"text\": \"Ilona\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Olympic moment\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly who\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"her message\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"Engelke\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can take the process a little slow and really look at who is aligned with her, who is the right brand partner.\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"the right brand partner\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's certainly hectic right now, but we will be somewhat strategic and slow because it is vitally important for Ilona being exactly who she is.\\\"\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\", \"score\": 0.9999999986521289, \"rank\": 1.3480749850994234e-09, \"text\": \"Ilona\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Mitrecey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly who\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"T. Bettina Cornwell, the Philip H. Knight Chair at the University of Oregon and head of the department of marketing, believes an athlete must go beyond building a social media platform to have real staying power.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3514, \"end\": 3521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bettina_von_Arnim\", \"score\": 0.999738844420431, \"rank\": 0.00026122286874423933, \"text\": \"Bettina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bettina_von_Arnim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bettina_von_Arnim\"}, {\"begin\": 3522, \"end\": 3530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\", \"score\": 0.9999991206004099, \"rank\": 8.7940017736557e-07, \"text\": \"Cornwell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Philip H. Knight Chair\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3558}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"Oregon\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"a social media platform\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3695}, {\"ngram\": \"real staying power\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3722}]},