am\": \"sport performance\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"a life story\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not to say that top performing athletes cannot have top follower numbers on social media, but to truly capture the heart of an audience, storytelling is essential,\\\" Cornwell said.\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 4155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4141, \"end\": 4149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\", \"score\": 0.9999991206004099, \"rank\": 8.7940017736557e-07, \"text\": \"Cornwell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Cornwell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top performing athletes\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4015}, {\"ngram\": \"top follower numbers\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4048}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4064}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 4087, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"an audience\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4111}, {\"ngram\": \"storytelling\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The more relatable an athlete is as a person, the more the audience will enjoy their unrelatable elite athletic performance - 'I do not know how she does it, but I love watching her!'\\\"\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The more relatable an athlete\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4201}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4224}, {\"ngram\": \"their unrelatable elite athletic performance\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the world today is fickle and meme-driven, said John Baick, a professor of history at Western New England University, who noted there is no way to predict how the audience will react to any athlete or viral moment.\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 